{"tid":2199512,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"S.H.E出道19周年沒合體 各自發文祝賀願相愛到老","createTime":"2020-09-12T09:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T05:43:17.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"719228ee2ea80d5ba85a795ff7ad15bf9ea91d59","tid":2199512,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"S.H.E出道19周年，3位成員任家萱（Selina）、田馥甄（Hebe）、陳嘉樺（Ella）各有發展仍保持着很好感情。她們昨日（11/9）似乎沒合體，但分別在社交網發文紀念，Selina貼上她們初出道的合照，留言：「《19年前19歲的我們》妳問我：『美好的愛該是甚麼樣子？』我說：『美好的愛，就是，我們的樣子。』S.H.E生日快樂，我愛你們」。<br />\n<br />\nElla就拍片祝賀，片中她說9月份是很溫心特別的月份，因為9月11日是S.H.E的生日。此時Ella的囝囝勁寶突然入鏡，Ella即叫囝囝一同說生日快樂，她又說臨近中秋節，所以選唱跟月亮有關歌曲《月桂女神》，即席獻唱幾句。她留言：「S.H.E生日快樂！解接跟勁寶先來一段懷舊一下。我們出道19年了，謝謝大家的祝福。」至於Hebe在社交網貼上很多emoji圖案，讓大家解讀，當中有3位婆婆圖案，寓意一直相愛到老。其中Selina和Hebe的貼文，五月天的阿信都留言祝賀她們19周年快樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/119071515_837033060436145_984844794430958731_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=WnIfiBDhTMUAX-3X5fL&amp;oh=8cc3b9dad6cf17afac989514999beafb&amp;oe=5F863F9E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F119071515_837033060436145_984844794430958731_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3DWnIfiBDhTMUAX-3X5fL%26oh%3D8cc3b9dad6cf17afac989514999beafb%26oe%3D5F863F9E&h=b6221f27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfa2e01d8232ac10269bfc901f573debc5d45916","tid":2199512,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://babyou.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/images/article/201801/lwfmnor.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbabyou.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2Farticle%2F201801%2Flwfmnor.png&h=4b7049df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛出道時曾上過《康熙來了》，Selina說，當初公司把他們三個湊在一起，還做了問卷調查，看大家個性怎麼樣，剛好他們三個都是不同個性的，公司想要將她們包裝成各自代表「溫柔、自信、勇氣」，才去翻字典替她們取英文名字，Selina代表月光女神；Hebe是春之神，Ella則是戰士、戰神之類的。<br />\n<br />\n當時小S問：「你們有沒有想過可以紅多久？」Ella毫不思索地回答：「大概兩年吧，等合約到了就差不多了。」<br />\n蔡康永急忙打圓場：「拆夥就可以紅更久吧？」Hebe直爽的說：「會死的比較慘！」嚇壞一旁的唱片統籌袁惟仁。<br />\n<br />\n話題越演越烈，三人竟然開始想，以後過氣了要做什麼，Ella說要賣早餐，為過氣後的生活找點樂子；Selina只想好好的當家庭主婦，Hebe則淡淡說：「隨波逐流吧，看有什麼工地秀要找我去，能唱幾首就唱幾首。」可愛的反應，讓蔡康永大笑：「人家才剛出專輯就問人家過氣的事情。」"},{"pid":"0595716a19be3402184e548b8113920a5065ade4","tid":2199512,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"不是已經沒有了嗎？"},{"pid":"2f5751a94531092db632fec3d4c28b1c5b6ef80e","tid":2199512,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0595716a19be3402184e548b8113920a5065ade4","tid":2199512,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"不是已經沒有了嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"唔明 🙄"},{"pid":"1df8346b0de46bf13c14676bdba13f0b36064bbd","tid":2199512,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jL6D7rqk4SQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjL6D7rqk4SQ&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=a21adb2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jL6D7rqk4SQ</a><br />\n諗返原來改編beyonce 🙄"},{"pid":"02a938254d1d4dc473e23517b28372340452e652","tid":2199512,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"當年邊個估到得ella 結婚生仔so called 最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052bde0684606827a53c68eafe308f42559c9cc6","tid":2199512,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"ella以前被定位做男人婆<br />\n而家好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652390e1d6bad05ca284987dd09e8a6b06b741ad","tid":2199512,"uid":33604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"052bde0684606827a53c68eafe308f42559c9cc6","tid":2199512,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"ella以前被定位做男人婆<br />\n而家好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"想當年，&ldquo;強姦S.H，放過E&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}